20:34.367 --> 20:37.570
* Mata ah-oo hima de *

20:37.637 --> 20:40.907
* Domo arigato, Mr. Roboto *

20:40.973 --> 20:48.815
* Himitsu wo shiri tai *

20:48.881 --> 20:52.419
* You're wondering who I am *
* Secret, secret *

20:52.485 --> 20:57.189
* I've got a secret *
* My true identity *

